                            <comment id="14459856" author="jstrachan" created="Wed, 24 Mar 2004 03:04:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bing - I think you&apos;d done most of the hard work &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Turns out it was just a flushing problem - that  System.out &amp;lt;&amp;lt; a &amp;lt;&amp;lt; b&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the first expression returns a Writer for the 2nd write operation, but no flushing was done. So this would have worked for you&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(System.out &amp;lt;&amp;lt; a &amp;lt;&amp;lt; b).flush()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve fixed the issue now using a flushing OutputStreamWriter derivation&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14460683" author="jez" created="Fri, 17 Dec 2004 03:19:54 +0000"  >&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;out = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; StringWriter()
out &amp;lt;&amp;lt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hello &quot;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;&amp;lt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;world!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
        
value = out.toString()
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; value == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hello world!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
        
out = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; ByteArrayOutputStream()
out &amp;lt;&amp;lt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hello &quot;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;&amp;lt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;world!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;

value = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;(out.toByteArray())
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; value == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;hello world!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
